(
  'Squat Pulses',
  'Kniebeugen-Pulse',
  'Pulses de Squat',
  'Squat Pulses target the quadriceps, glutes, and hamstrings, and also engage the core. This exercise involves pulsing in a partial squat position to increase muscle endurance.',
